    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "sometimes i just wish i could have a permanent escape. like, if i could just stop feeling this ache, or just be where he is. it feels so much more logical to just be with him than to keep doing this every single day. do you think it's wrong to feel like i just want to be done with all of this?",
